Package org.sbml.squeezer.io

This package contains all necessary classes for parsing and writing files.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IOOptions
    This is a list of possible io command line options.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SBMLio<T>
    A manager class for reading and writing models from some source into JSBML data objects and to synchronize the model with the original data structure afterwards.
    SqSBMLReader
    This class provides methods to create JSBML models independently from libSBML.
    SqSBMLWriter
    This class is a libSBML independent converter for JSBML models.

Package org.sbml.squeezer.io Description

This package contains all necessary classes for parsing and writing files. There are classes for writing LaTeX, reading and writing user settings and file filtering.
Since:
1.3
